            <ol class="privacy">
                <li><b>Overview</b>
                    <ol>
                        <li>
                            Protecting your information and maintaining your privacy are of the utmost importance to LinkMe.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            This Privacy Statement contains important information about:
                            <ol>
                                <li>What personally identifiable information of yours we collect;</li>
                                <li>How the information is used;</li>
                                <li>With whom the information may be shared;</li>
                                <li>How you can access and change your account information;</li>
