                                <li>with the suppliers of goods and/or services that we think may be of interest to you;</li>
                                <li>in connection with an acquisition or potential acquisition of an interest in LinkMe;</li>
                                <li>to the extent that we are required or authorised by law to do so; and</li>
                                <li>for administrative purposes including research, planning, service development, security and risk management.</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </li>
